  "detailed_description": "Welcome to the craziest chess-related experience you can find!<br><strong>Checkmate Kings</strong> is an <strong>action party game</strong> with <strong>twin stick shooters</strong>, <strong>bullet hells</strong> and <strong>2D fighters</strong> influences.<br>In this game, there is no health bar. If one chess piece hits you <strong>it's game over!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose your character from a roster of 8 kings and queens inspired by fictional and historical characters.<br>You'll find each of them has a unique personality and playstyle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>8 unique playstyles allow you to pressure your opponent however you like best!<br>Shoot, place pieces and dodge around to get the upper hand!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Placing chess pieces, dodging, and pressuring your opponent is not all there is to the game! <br>Gather <strong>crowns</strong> and use their power to <strong>steal </strong>enemy pieces!<br>Turn the tides <strong>in a single move!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you play you'll be able to unlock unique customization options for your arena!<br>Choose your favorite look and fill the stands with the best crowd you can find!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online and local 1v1 multiplayer!<br></li><li>Arcade mode!<br></li><li>Progression system with unique customization possibilities!<br></li><li>8 characters with unique playstyles!<br></li><li>Fast, hectic and fun gameplay!<br></li><li>Powerful pickups!<br></li><li>A unique and fresh take on the oldest game in the world!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to the craziest chess-related experience you can find!<br><strong>Checkmate Kings</strong> is an <strong>action party game</strong> with <strong>twin stick shooters</strong>, <strong>bullet hells</strong> and <strong>2D fighters</strong> influences.<br>In this game, there is no health bar. If one chess piece hits you <strong>it's game over!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/555342f02a4bb45051408e4f1055db75.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose your character from a roster of 8 kings and queens inspired by fictional and historical characters.<br>You'll find each of them has a unique personality and playstyle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/a62a6f146513e3641be200b92e382380.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>8 unique playstyles allow you to pressure your opponent however you like best!<br>Shoot, place pieces and dodge around to get the upper hand!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/fb952b520adf15f62586d9e04db2ebf6.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Placing chess pieces, dodging, and pressuring your opponent is not all there is to the game! <br>Gather <strong>crowns</strong> and use their power to <strong>steal </strong>enemy pieces!<br>Turn the tides <strong>in a single move!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.poster.avif?t=1686844934\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.webm?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646910/extras/d3f706db7082ba1adfdb588295c6b2cc.mp4?t=1686844934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you play you'll be able to unlock unique customization options for your arena!<br>Choose your favorite look and fill the stands with the best crowd you can find!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online and local 1v1 multiplayer!<br></li><li>Arcade mode!<br></li><li>Progression system with unique customization possibilities!<br></li><li>8 characters with unique playstyles!<br></li><li>Fast, hectic and fun gameplay!<br></li><li>Powerful pickups!<br></li><li>A unique and fresh take on the oldest game in the world!</li></ul>",
